name: Halftone Glitchy Cosmic Squid
description:
This is a still/saved image chosen specifically by me, of combined layers of an GIF animation I made in Procreate.

Inspired by psychedelics and so many interesting sounds/vibrations in music. So many dimensions and layers when you are in tuned with it all. Feel yourself sifting in and out… 


You might feel glitchy.

What is reality?
